2014年1月，單曲〈Nothing Left to Lose〉在美國發行；2月開始，地下天堂在北美進行為期兩週的單曲宣傳；緊接著則首度登陸澳洲，參加巡迴音樂節Soundwave <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sfmedia.com.au/soundwave-festival-interview-heavens-basement/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-01-11 |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111183122/http://sfmedia.com.au/soundwave-festival-interview-heavens-basement/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在澳洲各大城市表演。2月18日<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dingdongloungenz.com/news/official-after-parties-for-westfest-story-so-far-terror-and-stiff-little-fingers/ | title = Official After Parties for Westfest, Story So Far, Terror & Stiff Little Fingers（紐西蘭搖滾酒吧Ding Dong Lounge官方最新消息） | language = en | accessdate = 2014-03-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309211839/http://www.dingdongloungenz.com/news/official-after-parties-for-westfest-story-so-far-terror-and-stiff-little-fingers/ | archivedate = 2014-03-09 }}</ref>，樂團在抵達澳洲之前，順道經過紐西蘭，並在當地的Westfest揭幕派對兼The Story So Far續攤派對上表演<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dingdongloungenz.com/events/heavens-basement-uk-and-ekko-park/#.UxyPafmSwkN/ | title = Westfest Launch/The Story So Far After Party（紐西蘭搖滾酒吧Ding Dong Lounge官方活動頁面） | language = en | accessdate = 2014-03-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309211845/http://www.dingdongloungenz.com/events/heavens-basement-uk-and-ekko-park/#.UxyPafmSwkN/ | archivedate = 2014-03-09 }}</ref>，這也是樂團在紐西蘭的第一場演出。在南半球活動的同時，樂團入圍美國知名金屬搖滾雙月刊Revolver Magazine和樂器公司Epiphone合辦獎項The Revolver Golden Gods Awards中的最佳新人獎，消息也在官方臉書上公布<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10152207131179526&set=a.385520529525.163104.6153629525&type=1&theater | title = 地下天堂入圍最佳新人獎貼文（官方臉書） | language = en | accessdate = 2014-03-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://redbullrecords.com/news/2014/heavens-basement-nominated-for-revolver-golden-god-award/ | title = Heaven-{’}-s Basement Nominated For Revolver Golden God Award（Red Bull Records官方最新消息） | language = en | accessdate = 2014-03-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309212919/http://redbullrecords.com/news/2014/heavens-basement-nominated-for-revolver-golden-god-award/ | archivedate = 2014-03-09 }}</ref>。

2014年3月13日，樂團首次全歐領銜巡迴表演The Welcome Home Tour從英國啟程，途經愛爾蘭，跨足歐陸<ref>{{cite web | url = http://redbullrecords.com/news/2013/heavens-basement-announce-2014-ukeu-headlining-tour/ | title = Heaven-{’}-s Basement Announce 2014 UK/EU Headlining Tour（Red Bull Records官方最新消息） | language = en | accessdate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140209012820/http://redbullrecords.com/news/2013/heavens-basement-announce-2014-ukeu-headlining-tour/ | archivedate = 2014-02-09 }}</ref>。但由於巡演行程繁重，對主唱Aaron的聲帶造成負擔，4月1日，樂團在官方臉書宣布巡演於4月5日在德國波鴻提早結束，並取消該日後的所有場次，讓Aaron能夠充分休息<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?v=10152276909654526 | title = Welcome Home全歐巡演取消說明影片（官方臉書） | language = en | accessdate = 2014-04-18}}</ref>。5月10日開始，樂團將飛赴美國，參加一連串搖滾音樂節，包括[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]的Rock on the Range、[[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]]的Rocklahoma和堪薩斯市的Rockfest。

